{"tid":767110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話香港細嘅同我入黎","createTime":"2018-08-04T08:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T12:27:30.000Z","uid":82640,"like":32,"dislike":175,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"42e5f6985e6b0b386c986b13bffea76c21a92923","tid":767110,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"香港同亞洲其他國家嘅主要城市比較<br />\n其實完全唔可以話細<br />\n<br />\n香港vs首爾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/154112_0152f8f77b4b0f9cf23ba0b15de87769.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F154112_0152f8f77b4b0f9cf23ba0b15de87769.PNG&h=8292554d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港面積大約係成個首爾再加你半個仁川<br />\n<br />\n香港vs台北<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/154314_5328eca06ffba3c4417de4ffe70ea7c5.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F154314_5328eca06ffba3c4417de4ffe70ea7c5.PNG&h=e84e0aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港面積其實已經係大半個北北桃<br />\n<br />\n香港vs新加坡+新山<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/154608_0606c37635a4dcc23a857554a61879c0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F154608_0606c37635a4dcc23a857554a61879c0.PNG&h=fda62cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾所周知嘅例子，但原來新加坡加埋新山就會同香港差唔多<br />\n<br />\n之後就係真正黎料嘅時候<br />\n香港vs東京<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/154810_736c89d11ec2ede40eaefdcb45b8aebf.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F154810_736c89d11ec2ede40eaefdcb45b8aebf.PNG&h=92eaca75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港同東京23區黎比差唔多大<br />\n<br />\n香港vs紐約<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/155150_99881e2aa31797d775ee591c00bcd929.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F155150_99881e2aa31797d775ee591c00bcd929.PNG&h=3f03c8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港絕對係東方大蘋果<br />\n<br />\n香港vs倫敦/巴黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/155316_a8a3e51502e4ac3fdbc3806ebe6cb9a2.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F155316_a8a3e51502e4ac3fdbc3806ebe6cb9a2.PNG&h=a33af850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/155316_495e1a6e3777294d4310e2f786d4877a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F155316_495e1a6e3777294d4310e2f786d4877a.PNG&h=6ebfd369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同呢2個地方比，香港終於顯得細一啲<br />\n但都要注意返以單一城市黎計呢兩個係最大嗰兩個黎(唔計中國)<br />\n而且佢地市中心都係正中間<br />\n放射式向外發展<br />\n相反香港市中心偏南<br />\n再加上有西鐵呢類迂迴路線<br />\n出城真係世界第一<br />\n<br />\n日本人住得遠但間屋起碼夠大呀嘛<br />\n香港人連等收租嘅原居民都住到勁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於話香港細嘅人<br />\n你估真係要下下同北京上海比咩<br />\n佢地市郊好多人喺困住做奴隸咋<br />\n<br />\n其他參考<br />\n香港vs利物浦+曼徹斯特+保頓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/160325_2bdc84c019e57752053df1de2acf7883.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F160325_2bdc84c019e57752053df1de2acf7883.PNG&h=b8887a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗倫敦嘅英國城市同香港比收哂皮<br />\n冇可比性<br />\n<br />\n吳哥原來有2個港島咁大<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/160127_7a3e53c8243312a17f8ac5f8e15047a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F160127_7a3e53c8243312a17f8ac5f8e15047a6.png&h=980f6575&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a91b2617ce8a37f22adbacb15ef4bbf0f8312151","tid":767110,"uid":17641,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"細過深圳廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785ead92afee90e06caa8c4a57dc182493b315ed","tid":767110,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2119747a99cda51eab6ae9faa21175b2d7a1050b","tid":767110,"uid":82640,"like":41,"dislike":6,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"a91b2617ce8a37f22adbacb15ef4bbf0f8312151","tid":767110,"uid":17641,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"細過深圳廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"大而無當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23491eda415bdcfc7f970ecc0e1a90fb50eb5e0c","tid":767110,"uid":53026,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"人地無原居民、新移民、公務員係外籍等問題。"},{"pid":"cfa6fbad7bffd6680679831108d21a9ba8a3ace9","tid":767110,"uid":167289,"like":181,"dislike":2,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"唔細 但七八成係山<br />\n人哋全部係平地"},{"pid":"b337a55e2532f014c4335ca050645da509d5d955","tid":767110,"uid":82640,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"cfa6fbad7bffd6680679831108d21a9ba8a3ace9","tid":767110,"uid":167289,"like":181,"dislike":2,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"唔細 但七八成係山<br />\n人哋全部係平地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"中肯<br />\n<br />\n仲有不能自控嘅人口輸入"},{"pid":"06e746dc126599dea37f4c7aa53d22a1c5f41b61","tid":767110,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eab2c810fcad65fb119b3633f33e8f1f363af15a","tid":767110,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"06e746dc126599dea37f4c7aa53d22a1c5f41b61","tid":767110,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"