,"tid":767110,"uid":163350,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acd42ebe30c59a09d8b073caec5b8866fdae8896","tid":767110,"uid":27688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:27:49.000Z","msg":"其實香港唔細，無記錯紐約都同香港差唔多<br />\n當然香港水域都唔細"},{"pid":"0418143aaba29d6683cf14754d4196d94624f918","tid":767110,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e24af6da4f8374b282a19dc630b7aa87fb1b23f","tid":767110,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f02a03755b3fb5d2f4d8c3361a00dae4f66f196","tid":767110,"uid":164442,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eab2c810fcad65fb119b3633f33e8f1f363af15a","tid":767110,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"比起新加坡黎講<br />\n用地已經好fail"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951b9db5c1ac5d6b37afebb767f600be9907efd8","tid":767110,"uid":33213,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"cfa6fbad7bffd6680679831108d21a9ba8a3ace9","tid":767110,"uid":167289,"like":181,"dislike":2,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"唔細 但七八成係山<br />\n人哋全部係平地"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"人地國家揀地方起大城市都係揀一大片平地，容易發展<br />\n喺啲新建嘅城市尤其顯著<br />\n好似美國城市啲街可以畫格仔咁起<br />\n唔使煩地勢問題<br />\n<br />\n但係英國佔領香港嗰陣係冇諗過將香港發展成大都會<br />\n純粹係一個港口<br />\n啲英國佬就可以好似澳門葡人咁做吓土豪<br />\n<br />\n係清末以後嘅歷史發展先令到香港越嚟越多人<br />\n要喺一個本來唔適合起大城市嘅地方建設一個大都會<br />\n<br />\n你應該唔會搵到其他大城市<br />\n入面嘅主要區域係畀幾座大山隔開<br />\n要行山路或者隧道先去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2228fde4cec92d97070394fcefccceb506d160","tid":767110,"uid":7458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"但係香港人口密度好高"},{"pid":"4783e18ea79d0a9ef71f4b7136050dbb8501ead3","tid":767110,"uid":77277,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"951b9db5c1ac5d6b37afebb767f600be9907efd8","tid":767110,"uid":33213,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"cfa6fbad7bffd6680679831108d21a9ba8a3ace9","tid":767110,"uid":167289,"like":181,"dislike":2,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"唔細 但七八成係山<br />\n人哋全部係平地"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"人地國家揀地方起大城市都係揀一大片平地，容易發展<br />\n喺啲新建嘅城市尤其顯著<br />\n好似美國城市啲街可以畫格仔咁起<br />\n唔使煩地勢問題<br />\n<br />\n但係英國佔領香港嗰陣係冇諗過將香港發展成大都會<br />\n純粹係一個港口<br />\n啲英國佬就可以好似澳門葡人咁做吓土豪<br />\n<br />\n係清末以後嘅歷史發展先令到香港越嚟越多人<br />\n要喺一個本來唔適合起大城市嘅地方建設一個大都會<br />\n<br />\n你應該唔會搵到其他大城市<br />\n入面嘅主要區域係畀幾座大山隔開<br />\n要行山路或者隧道先去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"正解。<br />\n<br />\n香港咁撚多山<br />\n又唔炸尻左佢。<br />\n<br />\n死要行山，行你老味咩"},{"pid":"e940ad08f7ded7379594fc6efdb3fcdb014bdb27","tid":767110,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58b4fe16e670f767195a0faa7df48ad5c011f275","tid":767110,"uid":163350,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6d16db34fed8af157e40fe00dce4b054ad1bbc2","tid":767110,"uid":19676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"第一次聽日本人間屋大"},{"pid":"8fa8c7db768433d3f8f6708fecf67c289fc3f619","tid":767110,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ce55d7f48c417eadeb8da0f7963d35a20ff3e86","tid":767110,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"